videos.description: Devon Hall finds Jack Salt under the rim for the dunk.
videos.headline: Salt throws down early

videos.description: Virginia's Devon Hall drives and dishes to Isaiah Wilkins who slams it home.
videos.headline: Hall dishes no-look pass to Wilkins for slam

videos.description: De'Andre Hunter snags the ball from Frank Howards hands and breaks free for 2 points.
videos.headline: Hunter takes ball right from Howard's hands

videos.description: Ty Jerome hits his second 3-pointer from an NBA distance.
videos.headline: Jerome sinks 2nd from deep

videos.description: Ty Jerome chucks the ball full court to Isaiah Wilkins for the throw down.
videos.headline: Virginia moves the ball up the court for a Wilkins jam

videos.description: Oshae Brissett causes a Virginia turnover in the final seconds and flies through the paint to putback the third layup.
videos.headline: Brissett lays in third putback attempt for the Orange
